\n\n    <div class=\"zbnf-step\">\n      <div class=\"zbnf-step-num\">1<\/div>\n      <div class=\"zbnf-step-content\">\n        <div class=\"zbnf-step-title\">Cleanse your face & neck<\/div>\n        <p class=\"zbnf-step-desc\">Start with clean, dry skin. Remove all makeup and impurities so the device can work directly on your skin without any barrier.<\/p>\n        <span class=\"zbnf-step-tip\">Dry skin gives better contact and stronger results<\/span>\n      <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n    <div class=\"zbnf-connector\"><\/div>\n\n    <div class=\"zbnf-step\">\n      <div class=\"zbnf-step-num\">2<\/div>\n      <div class=\"zbnf-step-content\">\n        <div class=\"zbnf-step-title\">Apply serum or moisturizer<\/div>\n        <p class=\"zbnf-step-desc\">Apply your favourite serum or cream to your face and neck. The device's heat and vibration will drive it deeper into the skin for maximum absorption.<\/p>\n        <span class=\"zbnf-step-tip\">Hyaluronic acid or vitamin C serum works best<\/span>\n      <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n    <div class=\"zbnf-connector\"><\/div>\n\n    <div class=\"zbnf-step\">\n      <div class=\"zbnf-step-num\">3<\/div>\n      <div class=\"zbnf-step-content\">\n        <div class=\"zbnf-step-title\">Turn on & select intensity<\/div>\n        <p class=\"zbnf-step-desc\">Power on the device and choose your intensity level. Always start on Level 1 for the first few sessions, then work up to Level 2 or 3 as your skin adapts.<\/p>\n        <span class=\"zbnf-step-tip\">New users — start on Level 1 for the first week<\/span>\n      <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n    <div class=\"zbnf-connector\"><\/div>\n\n    <div class=\"zbnf-step\">\n      <div class=\"zbnf-step-num\">4<\/div>\n      <div class=\"zbnf-step-content\">\n        <div class=\"zbnf-step-title\">Massage upward for 5–10 minutes<\/div>\n        <p class=\"zbnf-step-desc\">Glide the device in slow upward strokes across your cheeks, jaw, and neck. Always move upward — this works with your facial muscles to lift rather than drag.<\/p>\n        <span class=\"zbnf-step-tip\">Use daily for 3–4 weeks to see visible firmness<\/span>\n      <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n  <\/div>\n\n<\/div>\n\n<style>\n.zbnf-htu { padding: 8px 0 4px; }\n.zbnf-htu-header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 24px; }\n.zbnf-htu-eyebrow {\n  display: inline-block; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700;\n  letter-spacing: 0.13em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #6B1A2A;\n  background: rgba(107,26,42,0.07); padding: 3px 12px;\n  border-radius: 100px; margin-bottom: 8px;\n}\n.zbnf-htu-title {\n  font-size: clamp(18px, 2.5vw, 26px); font-weight: 700;\n  color: #1A1A1A; letter-spacing: -0.02em; margin: 0 0 6px;\n}\n.zbnf-htu-sub { font-size: 13px; color: #888; margin: 0; }\n\n.zbnf-steps { display: flex; flex-direction: column; }\n\n.zbnf-step {\n  display: flex; gap: 16px; align-items: flex-start;\n  background: #fff; border: 1.5px solid #EDE4DF;\n  border-radius: 16px; padding: 18px 20px;\n  box-shadow: 0 1px 8px rgba(107,26,42,0.04);\n  transition: border-color 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;\n}\n.zbnf-step:hover { border-color: #D4A9B0; box-shadow: 0 4px 18px rgba(107,26,42,0.08); }\n\n.zbnf-connector {\n  width: 2px; height: 14px; background: #D4A9B0;\n  margin: 0 0 0 27px; border-radius: 1px;\n}\n\n.zbnf-step-num {\n  width: 34px; height: 34px; border-radius: 50%;\n  background: #6B1A2A; color: #fff;\n  font-size: 14px; font-weight: 800;\n  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;\n  flex-shrink: 0; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(107,26,42,0.25);\n}\n.zbnf-step-content { flex: 1; padding-top: 4px; }\n.zbnf-step-title { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; color: #1A1A1A; margin-bottom: 6px; }\n.zbnf-step-desc { font-size: 13px; color: #555; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 8px; }\n.zbnf-step-tip {\n  display: inline-block; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 500;\n  color: #6B1A2A; background: rgba(107,26,42,0.06);\n  padding: 3px 10px; border-radius: 100px;\n}\n\n@media (max-width: 600px) {\n  